Need to install vagrant:

  sudo apt-get install vagrant


Need to install ansible:

  sudo apt-get install ansible


Need to install an haproxy ansible module with:

  sudo ansible-galaxy install info.haproxy

Documentation for this module is at: https://galaxy.ansible.com/list#/roles/912


Neet to install an nginx module with:

  sudo ansible-galaxy install bennojoy.nginx

Documentation for this module is at: https://galaxy.ansible.com/list#/roles/2
